- Division of labor advocates: Specialization epistemically superior to generalism (Kitcher, Alexander et al.) (8 papers)
- Epistemic dependence theorists: Self-reliance often impossible/harmful (Nguyen, Buzzell & Rini) (6 papers)
- Moderate integrationists: Balance autonomy with appropriate reliance (Carter, Ahlstrom-Vij) (4 papers)
