  RELEVANCE: Shows how accessibility can create false sense of self-sufficiency and undermine appropriate epistemic humility. Relevant to understanding when "making it easy" encourages inappropriate DIY approaches rather than proper expert reliance. Demonstrates risks of underrating epistemic dependence.

